INSERT INTO public.tojung (id,num,total,jan,feb,mar,apr,may,jun,jul,aug,sep,oct,nov,"dec",created_at,nation) VALUES (362,'064','✨ 1. 2026 Overall Fortune
The year 2026 is like sitting under a bridge looking up at the sky—a year with limited vision and difficulty obtaining practical results. Achievements are scarce compared to efforts, often having name without substance and lacking real benefits. Like a fish losing water, vitality declines and periods of physical and mental discomfort continue. Many regrets will follow, so restrain desires and act cautiously. Parents'' health may cause concern, so check on them frequently, and unexpected harm may come from close people, requiring special attention to relationships. With an anxious mind and difficulty accumulating wealth, you may suffer unknown pain, yet amid this there is hope to overcome difficulties through cooperation and wise handling.

✨ 2. 💰 Wealth and Financial Fortune
Financial fortune in 2026 is extremely challenging. Originally lacking wealth blessings, achieving what you seek is difficult, and even when executing plans, desired results are often not obtained. January and February have particularly poor financial fortune, so avoid large investments or business ventures. April brings wealth opportunities from the south, so focusing there can yield small achievements. July may bring losses in trading and document-related problems, so carefully review contracts. October offers reversal opportunities where seeking small things may unexpectedly yield big ones—don''t miss it. November makes partnerships unfavorable, so pursuing business alone is better. Overall, this is a year to reduce expenses and focus on savings.

✨ 3. 🏆 Career and Promotion Fortune
