✨ 5. 🏥 Health Fortune
Special attention to health management is needed this year. Parents may suffer from illness, so frequently check health conditions and provide necessary help. You yourself may experience physical and mental discomfort and declining vitality, making sufficient rest and nutrition intake important. June and July may bring gossip if not illness, requiring both health management and careful speech. October brings a period when body and mind become peaceful, so restore health through regular exercise and meditation. Stress management is especially important, and appropriately utilizing hobbies or leisure time to calm an anxious mind is advised.

